	stock (ii) each of Goliath Film and Media Holdings directors and executive officers, and (iii) the Percentage After Offering assumes
	the sale of all shares offered. Unless otherwise noted below, Goliath Film and Media Holdings believes that all persons named
	in the table have sole voting and investment power with respect to all shares of common stock beneficially owned by them. For
	purposes hereof, a person is deemed to be the beneficial owner of securities that can be acquired by such person within 60 days
	from the date hereof upon the exercise of warrants or options or the conversion of convertible securities. Each beneficial owner’s
	percentage ownership is determined by assuming that any warrants, options or convertible securities that are held by such person
	(but not those held by any other person) and which are exercisable within 60 days from the date hereof, have been exercised.





	 





