	the nine months ended January 31, 2017, we completed and delivered Bridal Boot Camp and Merry Exes and recognized $169,300 of
	production costs as cost of sales. For the nine months ended January 31, 2016, we had no cost of sales.




	 






	Operating
	expenses






	 




